Package datingapp.program

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    Represents an Account object with an email and password
    ConstantKey
    this class has got a ton of constants to use in place of all the Strings that were originally being used as the parameters for the Person object to avoid any mistakes/confusion
    MatchRules
    sets up/defines the rules for the matching process
    Message
    constructs a Message object for the messaging system
    Node
    Represents a node of a DatingTree.
    Person
    constructs a Person object, which represents a user
    QuestionSpitter
    Returns a randomized list of questions of each type.
    SearchNode
    a helper class for MatchRules added to a HashMap that tells you who to match up each person with
    Tree
    Implements tree of nodes.
